values:
I finally got started on TWTYH holiday doujinshi contest.. I only got started on the cover of it though. -_- I haven't drawn anything in such a long time because I haven't been getting any inspirations, but now that I'm entering a contest, I've got something to motivate me. It's good to be able to draw again. ^_^ I'm also thinking about entering the Rising Stars of Manga contest... I've been wanting to ever since I first learned about it from Percy/Rem's website... but I never got to it. ^_^; I've been trying to come up with a story since last month but no luck.. I want something different... something.. out of the box.. a plot-twister... ........... Oh well. It'll come to me sooner or later! ^_^;

I watched Tokyo Godfathers two days ago. It's pretty awesome! It's funny, weird, and touching at the same time... o_o Speaking of weird.. I watched Excel Saga yesterday for the first time....... I didn't really understand it but then again, I don't think I was supposed to. ^_^;

Well, I can't think of anything else to say at the moment.. so I'm just gonna go work on the cover some more and maybe even attempt to spruce up my livejournal a little! >_<
